data.description: Welcome home to this sunlit  2 bed/2 bath,  penthouse level condo situated in  the conveniently located community of Waterside.   Home boasts a large, open floor plan with vaulted ceilings throughout. New carpet and vinyl flooring!!   Kitchen features neutral countertops, white appliances and a large breakfast bar that overlooks the  dining room and family room.  Family room is oversized and is ideal for entertaining.  French door leads to large balcony, perfect for your morning cup of coffee or evening glass of wine.  Owners suite is located off the family room and has a full bath and a HUGE walk in closet.  Guest bedroom and full hall  bathroom are located off the foyer.  Guest Bedroom features tons of natural light, a good sized closet and a door that accesses the hall bathroom for privacy and convenience. Community features a swimming pool, playground, tennis courts and walking paths. Home is conveniently located near major commuter routes  15/270/340 and also minutes from beautiful downtown Frederick's best restaurants and shops.  Additionally Wegmans, Home Goods, and a drive thru Starbucks are nearby.  Priced to sell and won't last!  NO CITY TAXES!!!
